  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>DESCRIPTION</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Walking In The Abyss is a horror and suspense game. In it you will be Jack Freydis, a confused and lost man in the middle of the storm looking for help or assistance. In this search, Jack will find a large castle, hoping to find some help, ends up finding himself in an unexpected and terrifying situation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RESOURCES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A castle to explore.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different monsters to face.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzles to solve.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>WHY BUY?</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A story full of mysteries and revelations. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Great experience with 2D horror. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help a solo developer. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VERY Cheap price.</p></li></ul>",
